An open-source Android implementation of a Bitcoin wallet, based on [[BitCoinJ]]. It was released on March 7, 2011 (1.1).

##External Links

* [(1)](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.schildbach.wallet) Bitcoin Wallet on Google Play.
* [(2)](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.schildbach.wallet_test) Bitcoin Wallet for Testnet on Google Play.
* [(3)](https://code.google.com/p/bitcoin-wallet/downloads/list) Direct download of test versions (also for Blackberry OS)
* [(4)](https://code.google.com/p/bitcoin-wallet/) project page on Google Code.
* [(5)](https://github.com/Goonie/Bitcoin-Wallet-for-Android) project page on Github.

